ynikami sprzeda\u017cy i rentowno\u015bci. Unikaj nadmiernych wydatk\u00f3w w tygodniach o s\u0142abszych wynikach, kt\u00f3re poprzedzaj\u0105 sezon szczytowy.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p>Podsumowuj\u0105c, wdra\u017caj\u0105c te proste strategie, mo\u017cesz zwi\u0119kszy\u0107 swoje wyniki sprzeda\u017cy, jednocze\u015bnie dbaj\u0105c o zdrow\u0105 rentowno\u015b\u0107. Pami\u0119taj, \u017ce kluczem jest elastyczno\u015b\u0107 i \u015bcis\u0142e monitorowanie wynik\u00f3w swoich kampanii.<\/p>\n<p><b>Masz wi\u0119cej pyta\u0144? Skontaktuj si\u0119 z nami.<\/b><\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<h2>Jak zoptymalizowa\u0107 wydatki na reklamy w okresach szczytowych?<\/h2>\n<p>Czy zastanawia\u0142e\u015b si\u0119, jak s<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":1,"featured_media":3801,"comment_status":"open","ping_status":"open","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":{"inline_featured_image":false,"footnotes":""},"categories":[3],"tags":[],"class_list":["post-3800","post","type-post","status-publish","format-standard","has-post-thumbnail","hentry","category-kampanieppc"],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"http:\/\/eubrand.local\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/3800"}],"collection":[{"href":"http:\/\/eubrand.local\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"http:\/\/eubrand.local\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"http:\/\/eubrand.local\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/1"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"http:\/\/eubrand.local\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=3800"}],"version-history":[{"count":0,"href":"http:\/\/eubrand.local\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/3800\/revisions"}],"wp:featuredmedia":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"http:\/\/eubrand.local\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media\/3801"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"http:\/\/eubrand.local\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media?parent=3800"}],"wp:term":[{"taxonomy":"category","embeddable":true,"href":"http:\/\/eubrand.local\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/categories?post=3800"},{"taxonomy":"post_tag","embeddable":true,"href":"http